    <h2 class="section-title">Seven reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Brand-specific code translation.</strong> Same alphanumeric, different brands, different meanings. We don't cross-apply.</li>
      <li><strong>Code is symptom, we diagnose the cause.</strong> Bosch E15 means flood sensor tripped, finding which leak is our work.</li>
